      <i data-lucide="chevron-right" class="w-4 h-4"></i>
      <span class="text-gray-900 dark:text-white">FAQ</span>
    </nav>
    <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4">
      Frequently Asked Questions
    </h1>
    <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 max-w-2xl">
      Everything you need to know about visa-sponsored jobs, relocation, and how our platform works.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="py-16">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4">
    <div class="space-y-4" id="faq-list">

      {# FAQ 1 #}
      <div class="card overflow-hidden faq-item">
        <button class="faq-toggle w-full flex items-center justify-between p-6 text-left" aria-expanded="false">
          <span class="font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white pr-4">What is visa sponsorship?</span>
          <i data-lucide="chevron-down" class="w-5 h-5 text-gray-400 shrink-0 faq-icon transition-transform duration-200"></i>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-content hidden px-6 pb-6">
          <div class="prose-custom">
            <p>
              Visa sponsorship means an employer is willing to support your work visa application for their country. The company acts as your sponsor, often handling the paperwork and fees required for you to legally work in their country.
            </p>
            <p>
              On VisaJobs.xyz, all listed jobs include some form of visa sponsorship or relocation assistance. You can <a href="/visa-sponsored-jobs/">browse all visa-sponsored jobs</a> to find opportunities that match your skills.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      {# FAQ 2 #}
      <div class="card overflow-hidden faq-item">
        <button class="faq-toggle w-full flex items-center justify-between p-6 text-left" aria-expanded="false">
          <span class="font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white pr-4">How do I apply for jobs on VisaJobs.xyz?</span>
          <i data-lucide="chevron-down" class="w-5 h-5 text-gray-400 shrink-0 faq-icon transition-transform duration-200"></i>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-content hidden px-6 pb-6">
          <div class="prose-custom">
            <p>
              Applying is straightforward: browse the <a href="/visa-sponsored-jobs/">job listings</a>, find a position that interests you, and click the "Apply" button. You'll be redirected to the employer's career page or the original job posting where you can submit your application directly.
            </p>
            <p>
              We recommend tailoring your resume for each application and highlighting your willingness to relocate. Check out our <a href="/blog/">blog</a> for resume tips and interview advice for international jobs.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      {# FAQ 3 #}
      <div class="card overflow-hidden faq-item">
        <button class="faq-toggle w-full flex items-center justify-between p-6 text-left" aria-expanded="false">
          <span class="font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white pr-4">Is VisaJobs.xyz free to use?</span>
          <i data-lucide="chevron-down" class="w-5 h-5 text-gray-400 shrink-0 faq-icon transition-transform duration-200"></i>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-content hidden px-6 pb-6">
          <div class="prose-custom">
            <p>
              Yes, VisaJobs.xyz is completely free for job seekers. You can browse all job listings, access our <a href="/resources/">resources</a>, read our <a href="/blog/">blog articles</a>, and subscribe to our newsletter without paying anything.
            </p>
            <p>
              We sustain the platform through advertising and employer partnerships. If you're an employer looking to post a job, please visit our <a href="{{ site.airtableForm }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">post a job</a> page.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      {# FAQ 4 #}
      <div class="card overflow-hidden faq-item">
        <button class="faq-toggle w-full flex items-center justify-between p-6 text-left" aria-expanded="false">
          <span class="font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white pr-4">How often are jobs updated?</span>
          <i data-lucide="chevron-down" class="w-5 h-5 text-gray-400 shrink-0 faq-icon transition-transform duration-200"></i>
        </button>
