        <div class="faq-content hidden px-6 pb-6">
          <div class="prose-custom">
            <p>
              If you're an employer or recruiter looking to list a visa-sponsored position, you can submit your job through our <a href="{{ site.airtableForm }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">job posting form</a>. We review each submission to ensure it meets our quality standards and includes visa sponsorship details.
            </p>
            <p>
              For questions about job posting or partnerships, reach out to us at <a href="mailto:{{ site.email }}">info@visajobs.xyz</a>.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      {# FAQ 7 #}
      <div class="card overflow-hidden faq-item">
        <button class="faq-toggle w-full flex items-center justify-between p-6 text-left" aria-expanded="false">
          <span class="font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white pr-4">What is relocation assistance?</span>
          <i data-lucide="chevron-down" class="w-5 h-5 text-gray-400 shrink-0 faq-icon transition-transform duration-200"></i>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-content hidden px-6 pb-6">
          <div class="prose-custom">
            <p>
              Relocation assistance is support provided by employers to help new hires move to a different city or country. This can include financial support for moving expenses, temporary housing, flights, help finding permanent accommodation, language classes, and sometimes support for accompanying family members.
            </p>
            <p>
              The level of assistance varies by company and position. Jobs on VisaJobs.xyz are tagged with specific relocation benefits when available. For more practical advice, check our <a href="/resources/relocation-tips/">relocation tips</a>.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      {# FAQ 8 #}
      <div class="card overflow-hidden faq-item">
        <button class="faq-toggle w-full flex items-center justify-between p-6 text-left" aria-expanded="false">
          <span class="font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white pr-4">How do I prepare for international interviews?</span>
          <i data-lucide="chevron-down" class="w-5 h-5 text-gray-400 shrink-0 faq-icon transition-transform duration-200"></i>
